#include<iostream>
#define llu unsigned long long int
using namespace std;
llu gcd(llu a,llu b)
{
if(a>b)
{
	if(b==0)return a;
	else return gcd(b,a%b);
}
else
{
	if(a==0)return b;
	else return gcd(a,b%a);
}
}
int main()
{
	ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);
	cin.tie(NULL);
	int t,n;
	llu ans,temp;
	cin>>t;
	while(t--)
	{
		cin>>n;
		ans=0;
		while(n--)
		{
			cin>>temp;
			ans=gcd(ans,temp);
		}
		cout<<ans<<'\n';
	}
	return 0;
}
